## Limitations

The findings are based on available online sources and may not capture the full scope of reasons behind fast food's popularity. Additionally, the data is primarily from U.S.-based sources, which may not fully represent global trends. The lack of recent studies in the dataset may also limit the current applicability of some findings. Further research, including updated surveys and global perspectives, would provide a more comprehensive understanding.